    slug: "flower-rehal-7-inch",
    description: `Flower Rehal 7 Inch is a compact and elegantly designed wooden book stand specifically crafted to hold the Holy Quran during recitation and study. The rehal — the traditional Islamic book rest — is an essential accessory in Muslim households and mosques, providing a stable and elevated platform that allows the reader to maintain a comfortable posture while engaging with the sacred text. This particular model features a 7-inch foldable design that makes it highly portable and convenient for use at home, in the office, during travel, or at the mosque. The stand is constructed from sturdy wood that has been finished with a smooth coating to protect it from wear and ensure longevity through years of regular use.

The distinctive feature of this rehal is its decorative flower motif carved or printed along the outer panels, giving it an ornamental quality that enhances its visual appeal beyond the basic functionality of a standard book stand. The floral design draws upon the rich tradition of Islamic decorative arts, where plant-based motifs have been used for centuries to adorn mosques, manuscripts, and everyday objects with patterns that celebrate the beauty of Allah's creation. The flower pattern on the panels transforms the rehal from a purely utilitarian object into a decorative element that adds a touch of Islamic artistry to any room where it is placed. The foldable mechanism allows the stand to collapse flat when not in use, making it easy to store on a bookshelf, in a drawer, or in a travel bag without taking up unnecessary space.

The 7-inch size of this Flower Rehal makes it ideal for holding standard-sized Quran editions, smaller Mushaf copies, and other similarly formatted Islamic books and booklets. The raised platform holds the book at an angle that reduces strain on the neck and back during extended reading sessions, and the angled surface helps to keep the pages open at the desired position without the need for the reader's hands to hold the book flat. The wooden construction provides a stable base that resists tipping, even when heavier hardcover editions are placed on the stand. The smooth finish prevents the book from sliding and also protects the cover and pages of the Quran from scratches that could occur on rougher surfaces. This Flower Rehal is suitable for daily personal use, for placement on prayer mats during individual or congregational reading, and as a thoughtful gift for Quran students, new Muslims learning to read the Quran, and anyone who values both the practical and aesthetic dimensions of their Islamic accessories.`,
    metaDescription: "Flower Rehal 7 Inch is a foldable wooden Quran book stand with decorative floral motifs. Compact, portable, and ideal for daily recitation."
